{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, all patients are not recruited or starting the intervention at the same time, but will all complete the 3-month intervention cycle.",
    "Inclusion criteria:",
    "1 Patients are ≥18 years old.",
    "2 The patients are permanent residents of Heilongjiang Province (annual out-of-home time less than 1 month).",
    "3 The patients all met the relevant diagnostic criteria for thyroid cancer in the Guidelines for Diagnosis and Treatment of Thyroid Nodules and Differentiated Thyroid Cancer, and were diagnosed with differentiated thyroid cancer by pathological examination."
  ]
}